{"tid":708213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"預備大陸化　由政府做起","createTime":"2018-06-19T07:21:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-19T09:20:37.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"44a6a0bdbbcd468f067ca68f1186fa79d6ab20d8","tid":708213,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T07:21:23.000Z","msg":"新聞說為了預備 2047，有國際學校將會大陸化，教普通話和簡體字。筆者非常同意香港人要預備大陸化，最好成間從國際學校改做大陸學校，那就 perfect 了。不過，最能讓香港人預備大陸化，還是要由政府帶頭做起。如果政府做哂以下五項，相信普遍市民都會舉五體贊成：<br />\n<br />\n1. 所有公職人員薪金不可高於中國國家主席，房屋醫療津貼亦跟內地看齊；<br />\n<br />\n2. 所有公職人員及其親屬改用中國內地護照，不可有外國國籍或居留權，亦不可有任何海外資產；<br />\n<br />\n3. 所有公職人員講話及開會用普通話，寫字及公文用簡體字，有錯或不標準者減薪，可累計。官員見記者、警察追賊和抄牌、鄉事派公開聚會等情況都包括適用。設公務員語文水平申訴專員，供市民舉報違者；<br />\n<br />\n4. 公務員新入職須考馬列主義、毛習思想、鄧理論、三個代表、科學發展觀，及中國歷史文化。現職公務員將來晉升時亦應考試。當然筆試用簡體字，口試用普通話，語文有錯或不標準扣分，可累扣；<br />\n<br />\n5. 主要公職人員子女在大學程度以前不可赴外國留學或就讀國際學校，須讀香港本地學校或在中國內地就學。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%A0%90%E5%82%99%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E5%8C%96-%E7%94%B1%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%81%9A%E8%B5%B7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%25A0%2590%25E5%2582%2599%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2599%25B8%25E5%258C%2596-%25E7%2594%25B1%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%2581%259A%25E8%25B5%25B7%2F&d=TJMO5HYnvvCHu4auIvl%2FpJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=4802cfad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%25A0%2590%25E5%2582%2599%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2599%25B8%25E5%258C%2596-%25E7%2594%25B1%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%2581%259A%25E8%25B5%25B7%2F&h=efc67ee9\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%A0%90%E5%82%99%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E5%8C%96-%E7%94%B1%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%81%9A%E8%B5%B7/</a>"},{"pid":"c3c890a6680c25de7bce0824a27cbe6221e98152","tid":708213,"uid":68598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T07:29:49.000Z","msg":"係就快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c4d20d28b80bf87c2079740c012ccac5b65a35d","tid":708213,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T07:30:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8f64d491c76a89e0fc057e912759936c5979de39","tid":708213,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T08:19:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔得公務員大大仲要用al 去京阪神玩咖"},{"pid":"226e8e21b474a94ee1adc200f8253cf0a0d566e6","tid":708213,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T09:20:37.000Z","msg":"快啦咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}